         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne bot. Garden ¶ 6/8/70. ¶  ¶ Accept my best thanks, dear Mr Bunce, for your goodness in sending the fresh Clianthus seeds. In response to your call I send now through Mr Rob Bird ¶  a case wit...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.08.06</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Daniel Bunce</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">MS MS SEQUENCE, Australian Box 4/1, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne bot. Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">6/8/70.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Accept my best thanks, dear Mr Bunce, for your goodness in sending the fresh <name key="Clianthus">Clianthus</name> seeds. In response to your call I send now through Mr Rob Bird<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Not further identified.</p>
               </note> a case with Conservatory plants, not many; yet you will see my good will at least. I am so <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">short-handed</hi>
               </seg>, that I cannot do much for others now, however much I may wish.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Whether I can after all respond to your kind invitation is very doubtful. The complications in my department involve so much <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">loss of time</hi>
               </seg>, that I am far less able than even formerly to muster spare hours. But I am all the same grateful for your attention &amp; that of your Lady.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Pray tell Mr Douglas<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Probably Alfred Douglass.</p>
               </note>, that I was <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">very sorry</hi>
               </seg> to miss his kind visit. I was on duty in the <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">industrial Museum</hi>
               </seg> when he called.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">With my best wishes your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Clianthus">Clianthus</name>
            </p>
         </div>
      </body>
